room_title: Escape room "Drago's Castle" by 5 Wits in Albany
room_address: 1 Crossgates Mall Rd Unit C107, Albany, NY 12203
room_description: We’ve opened the drawbridge on Drago’s Castle — an epic live-action adventure! But the dragon has escaped. And the princess needs your help recapturing him. See if you have what it takes to escape the dungeon, solve ancient riddles, discover secret passageways and chase down the giant dragon! Otherwise, there may not be a storybook ending...
